This paper discusses the efficient design of communication networks, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the tradeoff between transmission capacity and cost, which is related to optimization (cs.SI) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the impact of network topology and node capability scheme, which are related to systems and control (cs.SY) and computer engineering (cs.CE). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI, followed by cs.SI, cs.IT, cs.SY, and cs.CE.
